<p>We now enter the years from E2 to I2 to indicate the yearâ€™s we are interested in. My excel now looks like this â€“</p>
<p><a href="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-6_years.png"><img alt="" class="aligncenter wp-image-9858" height="309" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px" src="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-6_years-300x188.png" srcset="https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-6_years-300x188.png 300w, https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-6_years-768x481.png 768w, https://zerodha.com/varsity/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Image-6_years.png 854w" width="493"/></a></p>
