<p>As you can see, all the sheets except Sheet 1 are selected. Iâ€™ve not selected Sheet 1 since the sheet is already set up, and I donâ€™t want to mess with it.</p>
<p>Now, in sheet 2, I do all the above steps that we discussed, except â€“</p>
